    If a topological group <fr:tex>G</fr:tex> acts on a space <fr:tex>X</fr:tex>, then <fr:tex>G</fr:tex> acts on <fr:tex>G^{\Delta _n}\times  X</fr:tex> by
    <fr:tex
display="block">       g\cdot (g_0,\ldots ,g_n,x)       = (g_0g^{-1},\ldots ,g_ng^{-1},gx).     </fr:tex>
    We denote by <fr:tex>[X/G]_\bullet </fr:tex> the simplicial space

